---
title: Thai Beef Stir-Fry with Basil, Coconut Rice and Charred Snow Peas
description: Stir-frying is one of the best techniques for putting dinner on the table in under 30 minutes. We're upping the ante by pairing a Thai beef stir-fry with some DIY coconut rice - you won't believe how easy it is to make!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-beef-stir-fry-ee3e8fef.jpg
